Package: stattools
Type: Package
Title: Summary Statistics, Normalization and Visualization for Numeric Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Priyanka Kalyani
Maintainer: Priyanka Kalyani <priyanka.rkalyani@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of tools for computing descriptive statistics with
    outlier detection, min-max normalization, and visualization of numeric
    data using ggplot2. Designed for preprocessing experimental measurements
    in materials science and engineering research.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
